'''杆位获得者'''是指在F1比赛中以第一的位置（'''[[杆位|杆位]]'''）发车的车手，现在通常由在星期六举行的排位赛来决定。

<!-- Please do not change this to 69; although Schumacher was fastest in qualifying for the 2012 Monaco Grand Prix, due to his grid penalty he is not considered the polesitter --><ref name="Schumi">{{cite web |url=http://www.formula1.com/teams_and_drivers/hall_of_fame/7/ |title=Michael Schumacher |publisher=Formula One |accessdate=28 August 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070628195539/http://www.formula1.com/teams_and_drivers/hall_of_fame/7/ |archivedate=2007-06-28 }}</ref>[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]保持獲得最多杆位，目前為止共獲得100次杆位，[[迈克尔·舒马赫|迈克尔·舒马赫]]获得68次杆排行第二位。艾尔顿·塞納获得65个杆位列第三。塞纳还保持着连续获得杆位的最高纪录，他在1988年[[西班牙大奖赛|西班牙大奖赛]]至1989年[[美国大奖赛|美国大奖赛]]间连续夺得杆位。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/81898.html |title=The winning formula |publisher=ESPN |date=22 June 2012 |accessdate=7 July 2012 |first=Steven |last=Lynch |archive-date=2013-01-22 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130122092513/http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/81898.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>维特尔是最年轻的的杆位获得者，他赢得[[2008年意大利大奖赛|2008年意大利大奖赛]]杆位时仅21岁零72天。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/7613904.stm |title=Vettel on pole at rain-hit Monza |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=13 September 2008 |accessdate=2 September 2010 |first=Andrew |last=Benson |archive-date=2017-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731004748/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/7613904.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>最年长的杆位获得者是[[朱塞佩·法里纳|朱塞佩·法里纳]]，他获得1954年阿根廷大奖赛杆位时已高达47岁，79天。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/age.aspx |title=Pole Positions by Age |publisher=StatsF1 |accessdate=18 April 2011 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201839/http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/age.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

